+
+This feature verifies that Narrative Intelligence can produce pipeline-ready metadata.
+
+## Test
+
+```bat
+cd /d D:\Python\NTPE
+python launcher_narrative_intelligence_test.py
+python launcher_prompt_narrative_integration_test.py
+python launcher_pipeline_narrative_test.py
+```
+
+## Output
+
+```text
+reports\pipeline_narrative_test_report.json
+```
+
+## Purpose
+
+- Confirm Narrative Intelligence is usable by pipeline reporting.
+- Preserve literary, emotion, pacing, inner monologue, dialogue beat, and scene flow metadata.
+- Prepare for full pipeline quality metadata integration.